{
  "stem": "12666.3",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And look how-- what kind of an answer he got.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It's-- Because they had to make-- they had to make room in PW camp, they would take people to execution.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In particular, they would choose-- there was a SS report that I read, where in a PW camp, another group was arriving.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So they had to make room.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So they chose PWs that lost a hand or a foot-- you know, invalids.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they say, well, for invalids, we don't need a strong guard.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We can fewer men to supervise this execution.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So they drove outside the city.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They forced some of these prisoners to dig that big hole in the ground.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And there was one man per truck with a submachine gun to guard the prisoners.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Those were prisoners of war.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And what happened, it was winter, and the SS had a very heavy clothing.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And so one of the PWs jumped the German SS man and knocked him down, and took his submachine gun, and opened the fire against the other SS men.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And the other SS man had to jump into that hole to escape alive.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But many of them were shot, because these prisoners, they take the arm from the-- and they fled.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And so, this was a report written how several SS men were killed, he says, because of this-- and they describe the execution in detail, you know, the execution of PWs.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They themselves acknowledge that PWs were-- but the only excuse that they had is that Soviet Union has never signed the Geneva Convention.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So, therefore, legally, we couldn't do anything about that.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But it's interesting.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We had the document of Admiral Canaris, who was the chief of the German counter-intelligence.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I saw that.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
